						<summary>

						<p>A third pillar in the same place.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records that this pillar (on which this inscription is engraved) was caused to be made by a woman named Aḍaikkalamteḷḷaḷ, a member of the oil-monger community <hi rend="italic">(vāṇiyaḷ).</hi></p>						

